data.description: Welcome Home! Step into this beautifully renovated gem. As you enter, you'll notice the brand new windows throughout the home, complete with a transferable warranty, ensuring peace of mind for years to come. The abundant natural light that fills the rooms highlights the fresh and modern design.The new flooring adds a touch of elegance and durability, perfectly complementing the contemporary design. The electrical and plumbing systems have also been completely updated.This home boasts three spacious bedrooms and two full baths that have been remodeled as well. The large closets and ample storage space make it easy to keep your living areas clutter-free and organized.Situated on a corner lot with plenty of space for outdoor gatherings. Schedule your showing today!
